{"tid":824192,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"屌班新移民叫曬野食就咁走咗去","createTime":"2018-09-17T03:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T04:20:09.000Z","uid":98542,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4b6879576e0e6a7ff82aa023ae6bc0fa5448c5f6","tid":824192,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:42:55.000Z","msg":"啱啱打完風<br />\n自己本身係大專生有假放<br />\n所以走去陪老豆老母飲茶<br />\n去咗隔離公屋商場間酒樓<br />\n因為太多人就搭檯坐<br />\n對面坐咗對新移民夫婦<br />\n無意中聽到佢哋講話之後有朋友嚟<br />\n咁我諗住隨時調去第二張檯<br />\n點知過咗兩分鐘就突然唔見左人<br />\n留低曬啲嘢食係度<br />\n我成家O撚咗咀<br />\n屌你啱啱打完風你就咁樣浪費食物<br />\n大佬你知唔知道打完風D食材好難運入嚟㗎<br />\n你老味就咁走咗去<br />\n仲要坐係度嗰陣講「乜今次個風咁渣㗎⋯⋯」<br />\n仆你個街將你個肛門移植去你個口度喇<br />\n罪證：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/113852_bfbe51fa8c6b19fa97aadf4a47b3cdc1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F113852_bfbe51fa8c6b19fa97aadf4a47b3cdc1.png&h=23cb960e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4993321eb69f9f0f3a5426debddc53b3bab65d0","tid":824192,"uid":27234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"叫酒樓報警？"},{"pid":"91b3a68f2eede80bcc875fddc24276fecd5325e4","tid":824192,"uid":195169,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:48:04.000Z","msg":"已經想像到佢地用普通話講<br />\n&quot;我都沒有吃, 為甚麼要付錢!!&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f898dbea39b4f8b9a61cab2f293a20c47ec86919","tid":824192,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4993321eb69f9f0f3a5426debddc53b3bab65d0","tid":824192,"uid":27234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"叫酒樓報警？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"佢好似俾埋錢先走<br />\n屌依家D新移民好撚有錢㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737bd52993f501ef2e03297292c2589c4a2316ec","tid":824192,"uid":431